I learned a lot of things and most importantly the experience to compete in such a big event. I would like to thank my family, coaches, teammates, friends, and Indonesia federation @pbprsi for the endless support. It's been a pleasure swimming with the national team and world class swimmer from south east Asia. The future will never be certain. Independence day is all about the people. The people who sacrifice their life for this country. The people that live for the sake of other people. The people who lives for a greater reason. The people we called HERO. So, the person right there is my hero. A beautiful women standing in the picture starring at every challenge in the future and bad whispers of jealousy. She couldn't care less. Fear and weakness are not in her dictionary. She was the reason I can wake up every 4 am in the morning hoping that one day I will be one of the best. She is the reason I get all the achievements in my lifetime. She is the reason I become who I am right now. She is all the good reason in my life and my life has been a greater reason of her life. She's been my hero since my childhood and will always be. I cannot be prouder to call her, MAMA.
